  <section xml:id="sec-negative-binomial">
    <title>Negative binomial distribution</title>

    <introduction>
      <p>
        The negative binomial distribution describes the probability of observing 
        the kth success on the nth trial, where each trial has probability p of 
        success and all trials are independent.
